# Pong in C

This is a Pong game implmented in C using the SDL2 library.


## Setup (MacOS, Apple Silicon)
1. Download the SDL2 .dmg file here: https://github.com/libsdl-org/SDL/releases/tag/release-2.30.8
2. Open the .dmg and drag the SDL2.framework folder to your /Library/Frameworks folder
3. Download the SDL2_ttf .dmg file here: https://github.com/libsdl-org/SDL_ttf/releases
4. Open the .dmg and drag the SDL2_ttf.framework folder to your /Library/Frameworks folder
5. Run `make run` to compile and run the game


## Credits
